The paper also discusses the theoretical properties of the ACDC module, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper discusses the potential implementation of the ACDC module using lenses and diffractive elements, which suggests that it could also fall under the category of cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
